{"tid":2451484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BTS閃卡遭醜化慘被捱打 製作公司被轟歧視亞裔人","createTime":"2021-03-18T06:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T07:26:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d95c1d17b2c2d1d5595910940639b10fc82b5720","tid":2451484,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"紅爆全球的韓國男團防彈少年團（BTS）早前獲入圍第63屆格林美的最佳流行組合/團體，是K-Pop史上第一次有韓團入圍該獎項，不過於本港時間周一舉行的格林美上，BTS卻失落獎項，令全球fans大感失落。而近日BTS再次成為新聞人物，美國插畫卡片製作公司Topps以格林美作主題設計一系列閃卡，當中包括BTS，不過Topps方面卻遭到網民炮轟製作的閃卡內容是對BTS進行了苛刻的、種族歧視的描寫，引發了爭議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210318/NGBHDI5NNNDLDGFML75V4I2MYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210318%2FNGBHDI5NNNDLDGFML75V4I2MYY%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2dHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=ac1d604e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210318%2FNGBHDI5NNNDLDGFML75V4I2MYY%2F&h=3c661d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210318/NGBHDI5NNNDLDGFML75V4I2MYY/</a>"},{"pid":"0951dd6a95b448e0417ea184f4db826baceb2a92","tid":2451484,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"美式漫畫不嬲都核突 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f2cc759e3403392b71f57442724d4c98a353d1","tid":2451484,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"完左啦件事<br />\n好心d右派對準槍頭<br />\n明明係支狗攪肺炎出黎<br />\n拖埋其他亞裔落水真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMb0Yir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMb0Yir.jpg&h=bb0055e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2bd4d83219b8e1718546ced3ab961f3b05d1e0b","tid":2451484,"uid":96231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93f2cc759e3403392b71f57442724d4c98a353d1","tid":2451484,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c